### what is marxism?
marxism is a discipline which solve the problem that people have huge distinct assets cause by capitalism.
It was created by Marx in the 19th century in Germany.
And it has many methods to let human develope well, like watch things in two opposite ways, practice is essential and so on.
And it's one of reasons why China become a powerful country in recent century.

